The '''blue pearl''' was a [[Pearl/Legends|pearl]] found by the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]] in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]] under the surface of [[Sunshine Lake]] on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. He found the pearl inside a [[sun shell]]. When he gave the pearl to the an [[Unidentified finned amphibious species/Legends|amphibious sentient species]], it replaced the lost [[red pearl]] and helped grow the [[food pearl]]s they relied upon for sustenance.

